{"tid":1061702,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我個‘好朋友’成日當我狗咁撚","createTime":"2019-03-14T14:41:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T14:35:13.000Z","uid":7489,"like":0,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0d67e54fe8ef4f9aedae64715bf024a7a6a3ae5a","tid":1061702,"uid":7489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:41:56.000Z","msg":"講下背景先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我同佢都識左6年 <br />\n曾經都好fd 日日一齊返學放學 個個禮拜去對方屋企食飯 fd到連大家嘅屋企人都識得對方<br />\n自問對佢好好 因為我真係當佢係我最好最好嘅姊妹<br />\n<br />\n但呢半年佢唔知做咩對我愈黎愈怪 愈黎愈差<br />\n佢開始唔再同我返學放學 連食飯都唔會同我一齊<br />\n佢又識左新嘅best friend<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家淨係會搵best friend 一齊玩 <br />\n我呢?<br />\n無再主動搵我lu<br />\n不過我行理去撩佢傾計都會應下我嘅 不過一句起兩句止囉<br />\n好似由朋友變左去普通同學咁樣<br />\n<br />\n依家佢係有事求我/問我借野 先會同我好聲好氣講野<br />\n其他時候我一出聲佢就扮忙、扮聽唔到 或者用好煩厭嘅語氣話<br />\n&lsquo;唔得閒啊唔好搵我啦&rsquo;<br />\n最近仲發現佢同佢best friend會對住我細聲講大聲笑<br />\n問返其他人先知係講緊我壞話<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係好想留住呢份友誼 好想可以返番去以前咁 究竟我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60821b02431b021263ddb5904e1e12cd9d4cd904","tid":1061702,"uid":7489,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cb4748a12dc747187bb0d442895609b5502b113","tid":1061702,"uid":7489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:47:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/20.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec150a941aa48e8fd2ee278ad79b712c35d72223","tid":1061702,"uid":190714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"攤牌"},{"pid":"3d12dfe51bff4376593bc9ff28ca58b9692ea5bc","tid":1061702,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-14T14:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face